name: Sweetheart Tibbers Plush
description: Have you met Sweetheart Tibbers?

name: Elder Dragon Plush
description: The ruler of skies flies in as the softest dragon in Runeterra.

name: Moo Cow Alistar Plush
description: Alistar, the Minotaur is ready to lock horns in the softest of cuddles.

name: Gnar Plush
description: Gnar is the soft sidekick you've always wanted - so long as you treat him right (seriously, we heard he's got a little temper).

name: Featherknight Plush
description: The legendary Featherknight enters the fray, leading the rest of the Pengu into battle.

name: Willump Plush
description: A mythical yeti - Willump is here to carry you and Nunu to the most awesome of adventures that only best friends can have.

name: K/DA ALL OUT Tibbers Plush
description: K/DA's #1 stan.

name: Beemo Plush
description: It was a beeautiful day. Singing birds, fragrant flowers, and honeyed explosions filled the air.\nChuckling a particularly large bee turned toward his woodland friend, Turtle.

name: Rengar Collectible Plush
description: The Pridestalker is ready to pounce into your arms! Rengar is #05 in the Collectible Plush line.

name: Frostfire Tibbers XL Plush
description: Extra bear for extra warmth. Frostfire Tibbers XL Plush has been summoned to keep you warm with his long fur.

name: Warring Kingdoms Jarvan IV Figure
description: "By my will, this shall be finished.” \nWarring Kingdoms Jarvan IV brings a cataclysm to the Series 4 line as Special Edition #04 to celebrate the Lunar New Year.

name: Immortal Journey Irelia & Talon DUO Figures
description: Long ago, in an ancient land, many souls gathered beneath the gods to test the limits of their power. Foolish and arrogant, brave and just, their journeys are written into the immortal pages of history…\nIn the light of his hubris, dragon king Talon is challenged by demigoddess Irelia to a duel in order for him to see humility.\nThe epic duel between these two are now available as #01 in Series 4.

name: Cho'Gath Team Mini
description: Limited Edition Cho'Gath will feast upon the world and feed the souls to the Void.

name: Battle Principal Yuumi Team Mini
description: The newest principal of durandal God-Weapon Academy arrives as our newest Limited Edition Team Mini. As a powerful channeler of magic, she uses the academic registry book as a focus object to generate apocalyptic levels of energy... often while perched on a terrified student's head.

name: Corki Corgi Figure
description:
"That just goes to show you you're nothin' but a Whiskey Delta!"
\nCorgi Corki flies into the Series 4 line as Limited Edition #06 to celebrate this year's April Fools. Atop his trusty corgi, Corki is ready to start making his special delivery across Runeterra. This figure is a Limited Edition variant that comes with its own custom Series 4 Limited Edition box, usable in-game League of Legends Summoner Icon, and will not be restocked once sold out.

name: Zoe XL Figure
description: You'll never know where she will appear next as Zoe crosses dimensions to find her way into the Series 3 figure line as #06.

name: Yuumi Figure
description: "Where's my fishy fishy fish for my dishy dishy dish?" Yuumi, the Magical Cat zooms into the Series 3 figure line as #021.

name: Nendoroid Ezreal
description:
Who needs a map when you have this prodigal explorer to lead the way? We're excited to bring you this premium Nendoroid Ezreal figure, produced in collaboration with Good Smile.
\nPro-tip: Keep separate from Noxians. And you should probably keep him away from Shyvana as well.

\nNendoroid are highly posable and come with swappable arms and faces, allowing you to act out a variety of different scenes.
\nTilt the enemy bot lane with Mystic Shot and Trueshot Barrage add-on pieces.
\nAn articulated stand is included to support various poses.

name: Urf Figure (Series 3)
description: A golden spatula. Narwhals of glory. A wondrous olive crown. Urf is Limited Edition and the king of the Series 3 figure line. URF!

name: Yasuo Figure
description: One blade, one purpose. Cutting through like a Steel Tempest, Yasuo flows into the Series 2 collection.

name: Ahri Unlocked Statue
description: Innately connected to the latent power of Runeterra, Ahri is a vastaya who can reshape magic into orbs of raw energy. She revels in toying with her prey by manipulating their emotions before devouring their life essence. Despite her predatory nature, Ahri retains a sense of empathy as she receives flashes of memory from each soul she consumes.\nAhri, The Nine-Tailed Fox is now Unlocked.

name: Xayah Unlocked Statue
description: Deadly and precise, Xayah is a vastayan revolutionary waging a personal war to save her people. She uses her speed, guile, and razor-sharp feather blades to cut down anyone who stands in her way. Xayah fights alongside her partner and lover, Rakan, to protect their dwindling tribe, and restore their race to her vision of its former glory. \nXayah, The Rebel is now Unlocked.

name: Miss Fortune Unlocked
description: A Bilgewater captain famed for her looks but feared for her ruthlessness, Sarah Fortune paints a stark figure among the hardened criminals of the port city. As a child, she witnessed the reaver king Gangplank murder her family - an act she brutally avenged years later, blowing up his flagship while he was still aboard. Those who underestimate her will face a beguiling and unpredictable opponent... and likely, a bullet or two in their guts.\nMiss Fortune, The Bounty Hunter is now Unlocked.

name: PROJECT: Irelia Unlocked Statue
description:
"Let them come! This land will be their graveyard!"
\n Special Edition PROJECT: Irelia is now Unlocked.

name: Rakan Unlocked Statue
description:
As mercurial as he is charming, Rakan is an infamous vastayan troublemaker and the greatest battle-dancer in Lhotlan tribal history. To the humans of the Ionian highlands, his name has long been synonymous with wild festivals, uncontrollable parties, and anarchic music. Few would suspect this energetic, traveling showman is also partner to the rebel Xayah, and is dedicated to her cause.
\nRakan, The Charmer is now Unlocked

name: Ashe Unlocked Statue
description: Take a good look -- it's the last you're going to get. Ashe is now Unlocked.

name: K/DA Akali Unlocked Statue
description: You ready for this? K/DA Akali takes it to t he top of the Unlocked statue line as #009. This Special Edition includes a blacklight that shows off Akali's neon accents when shone on the statue.

name: Jhin Unlocked Statue
description:
Using his gun as his paintbrush, Jhin creates works of artistic brutality, horrifying victims and onlookers. He gains a cruel pleasure from putting on his gruesome theater, making him the ideal choice to send the most powerful of messages: terror.
\nJhin, the Virtuoso is now Unlocked.

name: Zed Unlocked Statue
description: The unseen blade is the deadliest. Zed is now Unlocked.

name: Katarina Unlocked Statue
description: Ready for trouble? Kat doesn't care if you are ready or not. Katarina is now Unlocked.

name: Kai'Sa Mousepad
description: Premium double-stitched mousepad features Kai'sa, The Daughter of the Void in her base splash art

name: Winter Wonder Soraka Mousepad
description: A kindly duchess within the court of the Poro King, Soraka's lands are filled with beautiful animals made of pristine, enchanted ice. These menageries stretch for miles, tended by her retainers.

name: Arcade Ezreal Mousepad
description: High-quality mousepad featuring Arcade Ezreal's splash art and an anti-slip bottom.

name: PROJECT: Jhin Mousepad
description:
Trace 10: PROJECT: Jhin. After a botched surgery, Jhin went from being a black-market augmented hacker to a notorious mechanized killer for hire. Still programmed with a taste for high-clearance upgrades, the tech Jhin takes from his victims has left him with a severe personality fragmentation, and a dark vision for the future of PROJECT... and humanity.

Features:

name: Minion "Battlefield" Mousepad
description: High-quality mousepad with an anti-slip bottom depicting the fight that rages on between minions on the battlefield.

name: Yuumi Mousepad
description:
Premium double-stitched mousepad features Yuumi, The Magical Cat in her base splash art.

Premium double-stitched mousepad features Yuumi, The Magical Cat in her base splash art.

name: Dunkmaster Darius Mousepad
description: High-quality mousepad with an anti-slip bottom featuring Dunkmaster Darius.

name: K/DA XL Mousepad
description: Make your popstar dreams come true with the band as they slay on this XL mousepad.

name: K/DA Album Art XL Mousepad
description: Ahri, Akali, Kai'Sa, and Evelynn are here to breakout into the scene.

name: PROJECT: Vayne Mousepad
description: Trace 11: PROJECT: Vayne. Augmented with classified tech, Vayne was once a member of PROJECT's counter espionage unit. After she was betrayed by the corporation she served, she now stalks the shadows as a vigilante, searching for ways to break PROJECT and the technology that haunts her soul.

name: Spirit Blossom Teemo Beanie
description: Be as mischievous as Spirit Blossom Teemo

name: Teemo Hat
description: We can’t guarantee that standing really still while wearing this Teemo hat will turn you invisible, but it never hurts to try.

name: Red Minion Hat
description: Join the red side in comfort with this incredibly soft hat.

name: K/DA ALL OUT Suede Dad Hat
description: K/DA returns with their new EP as queens of the music world.

name: Dunkmaster Darius Snapback
description: "Better call traveling because I'm going places."

name: Pool Party "Squid" Dad Hat
description: Get your pool party on with your favorite squid buddy.

name: K/DA AKALI SNAPBACK
description: K/DA AKALI SNAPBACK

name: Pool Party "Coconut" Dad Hat
description: Mmmm. Enjoy a tropical drink with a tropical hat.

name: League Comic Inspired Snapback Hat
description: Grab some League of Legends comic inspired style for your head.

name: Pool Party "Pineapple" Dad HatPool Party "Pineapple" Dad Hat
description: Nothing says delicious fun at the beach quite like a pineapple.
